<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('partials/head', { fullTitle, metaDescription, robots }) %>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header', { nav, meta }) %>

  <main id="main">
    <section class="hero" style="padding-bottom: 2rem;">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="confirmation-header">
          <span class="confirmation-check" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
          <h1>Payment received — Next steps</h1>
        </div>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">We received your payment for the <strong>48-hour Email Auth Compliance Sprint</strong>. Follow the steps below to get started.</p>
        <div id="reference-info" class="reference-info" style="display: none;">
          <p id="reference-text"></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="confirmation-steps">
          <div class="confirmation-step">
            <div class="step-number">1</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h2>Complete the Intake Form</h2>
              <p>This is required to start the 48-hour clock. Without the intake form, we can't begin work.</p>
              <a href="<%= meta.intake_form_url %>" id="intake-form-cta" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg mt-2">Complete Intake Form →</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="confirmation-step">
            <div class="step-number">2</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h2>What happens next</h2>
              <ul class="step-list">
                <li><strong>48 hours starts</strong> once you submit the intake form and provide DNS access (or confirm your access method).</li>
                <li>We review your current SPF, DKIM, and DMARC configuration.</li>
                <li>We set up or fix records as needed, with your approval for any changes.</li>
                <li>We verify pass/fail status using standard authentication checks.</li>
              </ul>
              <h3>What you'll receive:</h3>
              <ul class="step-list">
                <li>Proof screenshots of authentication checks (before/after)</li>
                <li>A summary of final DNS records and what changed</li>
                <li>Rollback notes (what to revert if needed)</li>
                <li>Basic unsubscribe compliance notes (for marketing mail)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="confirmation-step">
            <div class="step-number">3</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h2>What to prepare</h2>
              <p>Have this information ready for the intake form:</p>
              <ul class="step-list checklist">
                <li><strong>Domain name(s)</strong> — The domain(s) you send email from</li>
                <li><strong>DNS host</strong> — Where your DNS is managed (e.g., Cloudflare, GoDaddy, Route53, Namecheap)</li>
                <li><strong>Email platforms</strong> — All services that send email on your behalf (e.g., Google Workspace, Mailchimp, Postmark, HubSpot, your app's transactional sender)</li>
                <li><strong>DNS access method</strong> — Your preference:
                  <ul>
                    <li><em>Best:</em> Delegated/limited DNS access (you add us temporarily)</li>
                    <li><em>Good:</em> Screen-share where you make changes with our guidance</li>
                    <li><em>Avoid:</em> Sharing passwords (we don't recommend this)</li>
                  </ul>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="confirmation-step">
            <div class="step-number">4</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h2>Communication</h2>
              <p>Updates will be sent to the email you provided during checkout.</p>
              <ul class="step-list">
                <li><strong>Support email:</strong> <a href="mailto:<%= meta.contact_email %>" id="support-email-link"><%= meta.contact_email %></a></li>
                <li><strong>Response time:</strong> Within 1 business day (often faster)</li>
                <li>If you have questions or need to update your intake info, just reply to any email from us.</li>
              </ul>
              <p id="client-email-notice" style="display: none;"></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="notice-box notice-box-warning mt-3">
          <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Important notes</h3>
          <ul class="mb-0">
            <li><strong>No inbox placement guarantee:</strong> This service provides email authentication setup (SPF/DKIM/DMARC) and objective verification. We do not promise or guarantee inbox placement, open rates, or deliverability improvements.</li>
            <li><strong>Legitimate senders only:</strong> By proceeding, you confirm that you are a legitimate sender (opt-in subscribers, customers, or users with lawful basis to email). We do not support spam or illicit email practices.</li>
            <li><strong>Bought by mistake?</strong> If you need a refund before work begins, email us immediately. See our <a href="/refund/">Refund Policy</a> for details.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center mt-3">
          <p class="text-muted mb-2">Ready? Start by completing the intake form:</p>
          <a href="<%= meta.intake_form_url %>" id="intake-form-cta-bottom" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Complete Intake Form →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer', { nav, meta }) %>
  <script src="/assets/site.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
